## When the playbook is NOT needed
- A pure read-only question ("what does module X do?") — answer from `MODULE-INDEX.md` / the code, no taskctl cycle.
- An orchestration-repo doc edit / small change — a direct edit (but a push to this repo's `{{PR_TARGET}}` is after a secret-scan).
- For a bugfix / feature / refactor in the target — the full cycle (worktree → review → PR with approve).

